WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
♪You're always♪

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:48.120
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 6=

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:49.649
Yu,

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:51.820
I booked your favorite restaurant today.

00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:52.930
How do you like it?

00:00:58.570 --> 00:00:59.570
Captain Shen,

00:00:59.930 --> 00:01:01.330
there's no need for you

00:01:01.370 --> 00:01:02.740
to keep standing there.

00:01:04.540 --> 00:01:06.579
As Miss Mu's personal bodyguard,

00:01:06.580 --> 00:01:07.849
protecting her at all times

00:01:07.850 --> 00:01:09.010
is my responsibility.

00:01:12.460 --> 00:01:13.329
Looking at it that way,

00:01:13.330 --> 00:01:14.099
Captain Shen,

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:15.700
you are indeed very dedicated.

00:01:16.210 --> 00:01:17.650
I see you everywhere.

00:01:18.020 --> 00:01:19.220
You just couldn't stay away.

00:01:19.300 --> 00:01:21.700
I also see you quite often, Mr. He.

00:01:21.850 --> 00:01:22.980
Speaking of which,

00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:24.730
you are not on the security team,

00:01:25.380 --> 00:01:26.980
yet you are more
dedicated than a bodyguard.

00:01:31.250 --> 00:01:32.450
How about

00:01:32.660 --> 00:01:33.849
you sit down and join us?

00:01:33.850 --> 00:01:34.730
No problem.

00:01:53.020 --> 00:01:53.930
Miss Mu,

00:01:54.330 --> 00:01:55.129
I suggest

00:01:55.130 --> 00:01:56.860
you eat more carrots.

00:01:57.900 --> 00:01:59.010
Captain Shen,

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:00.500
there's something you don't know.

00:02:00.900 --> 00:02:02.899
Yu hasn't liked carrots
since she was a child.

00:02:02.900 --> 00:02:04.140
I've always been the one

00:02:04.300 --> 00:02:05.700
to eat her carrots for her.

00:02:07.820 --> 00:02:09.970
So the reason her night blindness
hasn't been cured yet

00:02:10.140 --> 00:02:12.370
is that you've eaten all her carrots.

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:13.850
Night blindness?

00:02:14.460 --> 00:02:15.410
Yu,

00:02:15.420 --> 00:02:17.180
is your night blindness
still not better?

00:02:19.140 --> 00:02:20.690
What night blindness?

00:02:21.330 --> 00:02:22.459
What's wrong with you today?

00:02:22.460 --> 00:02:23.900
Why are you so distracted?

00:02:26.490 --> 00:02:27.690
Earlier,

00:02:27.700 --> 00:02:30.740
I gave my word
to Xu Mingzhu and the board.

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:33.019
I said I would definitely

00:02:33.020 --> 00:02:34.899
hold an exclusive auction with Hong.

00:02:34.900 --> 00:02:36.930
(So she's worried about this.)

00:02:38.530 --> 00:02:39.329
But

00:02:39.330 --> 00:02:42.020
there's very little official
information disclosed for Hong.

00:02:42.460 --> 00:02:44.580
He rarely attends any events.

00:02:44.980 --> 00:02:46.970
And I even ruined his painting before.

00:02:48.580 --> 00:02:51.370
No matter how I look at it,
this is on "Heck Mode."

00:02:52.460 --> 00:02:53.650
From the sound of it,

00:02:53.770 --> 00:02:54.899
Hong

00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:56.780
seems like a hot potato.

00:02:57.090 --> 00:02:58.690
Do you really have to work with him?

00:02:59.700 --> 00:03:01.500
What would a layman like you know?

00:03:02.210 --> 00:03:03.609
Hong's paintings

00:03:03.610 --> 00:03:05.649
are undoubtedly the best

00:03:05.650 --> 00:03:07.250
among Chinese-style art today.

00:03:07.490 --> 00:03:08.299
For someone like him,

00:03:08.300 --> 00:03:10.370
it's normal to have
a bit of a personality.

00:03:11.700 --> 00:03:12.609
Now,

00:03:12.610 --> 00:03:14.130
I need to consider

00:03:14.490 --> 00:03:16.620
how to establish contact with him.

00:03:16.700 --> 00:03:17.690
Yu,

00:03:17.770 --> 00:03:19.609
I can help find
the address of Hong's studio

00:03:19.610 --> 00:03:20.650
and send it to you.

00:03:20.810 --> 00:03:22.209
You can pay him a visit.

00:03:22.210 --> 00:03:23.459
With your talent,

00:03:23.460 --> 00:03:24.810
you might have a chance.

00:03:27.900 --> 00:03:29.780
(What a "genius.")

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:38.809
(Hong Art Studio)

00:03:38.810 --> 00:03:40.690
Are you sure this is the right address?

00:03:41.260 --> 00:03:42.650
I'm sorry, Yu.

00:03:42.810 --> 00:03:45.370
Something very important
came up at the office today.

00:03:45.980 --> 00:03:46.899
Otherwise,

00:03:46.900 --> 00:03:48.810
I would have definitely come with you.

00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:52.060
It's fine.

00:03:52.260 --> 00:03:53.370
I'll keep looking.

00:03:54.860 --> 00:03:55.649
He Min,

00:03:55.650 --> 00:03:57.250
thanks for the address.

00:03:57.420 --> 00:03:59.250
I've already found Hong's studio.

00:04:00.940 --> 00:04:05.019
♪The breeze gently stirs my heart
that longs for you♪

00:04:05.020 --> 00:04:06.489
(Such a familiar scent.)

00:04:06.490 --> 00:04:07.970
(It's been a long time.)

00:04:08.980 --> 00:04:10.920
(He really is
a Chinese-style art master.)

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:12.609
(The studio
has such a strong artistic vibe.)

00:04:12.610 --> 00:04:15.130
(I really hope I can meet Mr. Hong.)

00:04:17.580 --> 00:04:19.179
♪Flowers bloom many times♪

00:04:19.180 --> 00:04:20.309
Miss,

00:04:20.310 --> 00:04:22.259
♪The rain falls silently♪

00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:23.409
can I help you?

00:04:23.410 --> 00:04:24.379
Hello.

00:04:24.380 --> 00:04:25.849
I'm Mu Zhiyu, the Business Director

00:04:25.850 --> 00:04:27.050
of Mu Group.

00:04:27.090 --> 00:04:28.410
Do you have an appointment?

00:04:28.530 --> 00:04:29.529
As far as I know,

00:04:29.530 --> 00:04:31.499
Mr. Hong doesn't accept appointments.

00:04:31.500 --> 00:04:32.409
That's why

00:04:32.410 --> 00:04:33.579
I came directly.

00:04:33.580 --> 00:04:34.289
That's true,

00:04:34.290 --> 00:04:36.970
but we also don't accept
visitors without an appointment.

00:04:37.060 --> 00:04:38.259
This is a private area.

00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:40.140
Unauthorized people
aren't allowed to enter.

00:04:49.210 --> 00:04:50.290
Bo...

00:04:59.650 --> 00:05:00.939
Miss,

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:02.530
are you talking to me?

00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:04.900
It's such a hot day.

00:05:05.210 --> 00:05:06.259
Miss Mu, right?

00:05:06.260 --> 00:05:07.380
Please come in.

00:05:17.210 --> 00:05:18.460
Please have a seat, Miss Mu.

00:05:24.020 --> 00:05:25.059
My name is Yan Muqing.

00:05:25.060 --> 00:05:26.940
I'm Mr. Hong's personal assistant.

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:28.819
Since Mr. Hong is on vacation overseas,

00:05:28.820 --> 00:05:30.379
all studio matters

00:05:30.380 --> 00:05:31.970
are temporarily being handled by me.

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:34.819
I'm not sure what brings
you here today, Miss Mu.

00:05:34.820 --> 00:05:36.610
I'm very sorry for the intrusion.

00:05:36.820 --> 00:05:38.410
The reason I'm here today...

00:05:38.530 --> 00:05:40.259
First, because Mu Group

00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:42.139
accidentally damaged
Mr. Hong's painting,

00:05:42.140 --> 00:05:43.530
I've come specifically to apologize.

00:05:43.850 --> 00:05:44.379
I hope

00:05:44.380 --> 00:05:46.170
Mr. Hong can forgive us.

00:05:52.970 --> 00:05:55.259
This is our group's
new Head of Security.

00:05:55.260 --> 00:05:55.969
Today,

00:05:55.970 --> 00:05:58.140
he's accompanying me to visit Mr. Hong.

00:06:00.700 --> 00:06:01.850
(Head of Security?)

00:06:01.900 --> 00:06:03.780
(Boss, you really
know how to play along.)

00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:06.090
These gifts

00:06:06.140 --> 00:06:08.260
were prepared by Mu Group.

00:06:08.530 --> 00:06:09.610
Please accept them.

00:06:10.460 --> 00:06:11.820
Thank you, Miss Mu.

00:06:13.170 --> 00:06:14.460
Second,

00:06:15.090 --> 00:06:18.090
I'd like to make up for the
previous mistake on behalf of Mu Group

00:06:18.210 --> 00:06:19.699
by collaborating with Mr. Hong

00:06:19.700 --> 00:06:20.619
to hold

00:06:20.620 --> 00:06:21.820
an exclusive auction.

00:06:22.700 --> 00:06:24.380
An exclusive auction?

00:06:30.330 --> 00:06:32.899
I can't make the decision on this.

00:06:32.900 --> 00:06:33.499
But

00:06:33.500 --> 00:06:36.059
I'll inform
Mr. Hong of the Mu Group's proposal

00:06:36.060 --> 00:06:37.260
and wait for his reply.

00:06:37.820 --> 00:06:39.380
Thanks, Miss Yan.

00:06:41.410 --> 00:06:42.579
When I was coming up,

00:06:42.580 --> 00:06:44.940
I noticed the decor here
is quite interesting.

00:06:45.020 --> 00:06:46.699
Could I have a look around?

00:06:46.700 --> 00:06:47.409
No problem.

00:06:47.410 --> 00:06:48.650
Please feel free.

00:07:01.820 --> 00:07:02.820
Miss Mu.

00:07:07.970 --> 00:07:09.169
What are you doing?

00:07:09.170 --> 00:07:10.290
I'm staying with you.

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:12.090
Shen Jibai, what's wrong with you?

00:07:12.460 --> 00:07:14.899
What could happen if I just look around?

00:07:14.900 --> 00:07:16.169
That's hard to say.

00:07:16.170 --> 00:07:17.649
After all, a certain lady

00:07:17.650 --> 00:07:19.410
tends to have a lot of accidents.

00:07:20.060 --> 00:07:23.940
What if I lost my job because
I took my eyes off you for a second?

00:07:26.620 --> 00:07:27.380
After you.

00:07:38.410 --> 00:07:40.170
Thank you for today, Miss Yan.

00:07:40.410 --> 00:07:42.579
If there's any news from Mr. Hong,

00:07:42.580 --> 00:07:43.969
please let me know.

00:07:43.970 --> 00:07:44.970
Will do.

00:07:46.460 --> 00:07:47.730
Pardon me,

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:48.899
I'd like to ask

00:07:48.900 --> 00:07:51.290
this gentleman for some help.

00:07:52.260 --> 00:07:53.820
Oh, it's like this.

00:07:53.940 --> 00:07:55.579
Our studio's surveillance system

00:07:55.580 --> 00:07:57.089
seems to have developed a small issue.

00:07:57.090 --> 00:07:59.329
Since you're
the Head of Security for Mu Group,

00:07:59.330 --> 00:08:00.819
I assume you're quite knowledgeable.

00:08:00.820 --> 00:08:02.380
So I'd like to ask for your help.

00:08:03.330 --> 00:08:04.329
Well...

00:08:04.330 --> 00:08:05.850
It's just a small favor.

00:08:06.530 --> 00:08:09.170
Helping Miss Yan shouldn't be a problem.

00:08:10.970 --> 00:08:12.780
Then, I'll wait for you here.

00:08:13.090 --> 00:08:14.090
This way, please.

00:08:22.410 --> 00:08:23.289
Boss,

00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:24.289
I was about to burst.

00:08:24.290 --> 00:08:26.020
What's going on with you?

00:08:26.060 --> 00:08:28.259
You're the president
of the Security Group,

00:08:28.260 --> 00:08:29.329
and yet you're on vacation

00:08:29.330 --> 00:08:31.460
acting as a bodyguard for Miss Mu?

00:08:33.570 --> 00:08:35.250
You haven't fallen for her, have you?

00:08:35.260 --> 00:08:36.540
Don't talk nonsense.

00:08:39.050 --> 00:08:41.850
I obviously have
more important things to do.

00:08:43.450 --> 00:08:45.250
Does she know that you're Hong?

00:08:48.100 --> 00:08:48.689
Boss,

00:08:48.690 --> 00:08:50.379
can you give me a heads-up next time?

00:08:50.380 --> 00:08:51.569
I almost blew it just now.

00:08:51.570 --> 00:08:52.770
Alright,

00:08:52.930 --> 00:08:55.259
I'll explain everything to you later.

00:08:55.260 --> 00:08:56.420
Right now,

00:08:57.140 --> 00:08:57.769
look into

00:08:57.770 --> 00:08:58.850
this for me.

00:08:59.620 --> 00:09:00.619
Boss,

00:09:00.620 --> 00:09:03.220
you're hiding behind so many layers
when you're with her.

00:09:03.530 --> 00:09:04.770
Don't you find it exhausting?

00:09:17.830 --> 00:09:22.060
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:26.569
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:09:26.570 --> 00:09:31.060
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:39.540
♪Shadows move around♪

00:09:39.630 --> 00:09:43.829
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:09:43.830 --> 00:09:48.360
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:57.750
♪Don't slip away♪

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:04.769
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:04.770 --> 00:10:09.169
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:09.170 --> 00:10:13.490
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:13.510 --> 00:10:17.490
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:22.269
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:22.270 --> 00:10:26.599
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:30.909
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:37.060
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪